Text: Chargers Soccer Team Party and Trophy Charger Parents Our end of season party will be after our last game on Sat Nov th am game at Firetruck Park in Southside Place Treats and trophies for the kids will be handed out as well as gifts for the coach and asst coach In case of rain we will meet at Skeeters for lunch that day at I will be collecting from everyone at the next game to cover the cost of the trophies and gifts Or you can send it to me at Rice Blvd Hou If you have any questions call me at Go Chargers Deborah Martin Team Parent
